Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.46,0:00:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接着在热好的平底锅上倒入油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.57,0:00:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.63,0:00:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放油时要先把锅子\N从火上拿开才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.64,0:00:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.54,0:00:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在不是看煮菜节目的时候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.61,0:00:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以为是因为谁的关系\N才变成这样的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.05,0:00:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是谁呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.35,0:00:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是你，就是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.73,0:00:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,银河天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.07,0:00:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么？为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.14,0:00:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危机，这下糟糕了\N紧张！紧张！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.81,0:00:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,扑克光线BURU  BURU
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.75,0:00:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙大骚动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.11,0:00:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OK，胡闹一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.85,0:00:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也没关系，吃个饮茶\N好啊！好啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.62,0:01:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱着欢悦的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.86,0:01:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最后一起向神明祈祷吧\NBANG  BANG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.16,0:01:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因果报应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.56,0:01:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每天都是冒险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.30,0:01:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一旦开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.24,0:01:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就让它顺其自然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.84,0:01:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有机关，没有魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.31,0:01:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孤注一掷的I.N.G.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.61,0:01:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无忧无虑的狂欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.15,0:01:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梦想与希望的机关枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.05,0:01:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,锁定想要的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.16,0:01:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,BANG  BANG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.32,0:01:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跳舞吧，玩吧，BRAVO！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.03,0:01:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐上令人兴奋的火箭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.70,0:01:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开辟天下无敌的成功之路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.28,0:01:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(废校的回忆肉酱，海盗风味)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.28,0:02:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家好\N我是莱格．克莱兹曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.35,0:02:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,欢迎光临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.15,0:02:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,克莱兹曼侯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.66,0:02:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您想委托我们天使队做的工作是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.56,0:02:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,学生证吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.70,0:02:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.73,0:02:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原本在小学毕业时就该还的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.67,0:02:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,结果不小心错失归还的机会\N而一直留在我这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.44,0:02:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把学生证还给“回忆小学”\N就可以了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.15,0:02:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以麻烦你们吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.75,0:02:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你自己还就行了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.48,0:02:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.18,0:02:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那样就不能赚钱了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.22,0:02:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说的那间小学是在哪里呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.32,0:02:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在  “谜之区”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.83,0:02:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.66,0:02:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已准备一笔相当的酬金了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.16,0:02:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是钱的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.00,0:02:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.83,0:02:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"谜之七"？\N那是很危险的地方吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.64,0:02:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是海盗的温床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.57,0:02:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,温床？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.84,0:03:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思，克莱兹曼侯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.88,0:03:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么危险的区域\N我们是不可能去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.58,0:03:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.58,0:03:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,错失归还学生证的时机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.25,0:03:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我心里一直觉得很遗憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.25,0:03:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样的话\N我到死都无法安心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.86,0:03:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,克莱兹曼侯爵请放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.50,0:03:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这张学生证
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.94,0:03:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定会帮您送到\N您的母校“回忆小学”  去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.71,0:03:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.08,0:03:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.71,0:03:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里看起来好危险喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.12,0:03:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像随时都会有东西飞过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.99,0:03:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,克莱兹曼侯爵刚刚去世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.06,0:03:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.73,0:03:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,克莱兹曼侯爵...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.43,0:03:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么办呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.77,0:04:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为委托人去世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.94,0:04:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以不履行任务而回基地\N也是可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.71,0:04:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.74,0:04:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么危险的地方\N我想快点离开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.91,0:04:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.78,0:04:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且\N那个叔叔好像很烦恼的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.48,0:04:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要一个人去吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.95,0:04:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有兰花在的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.39,0:04:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这台机器也不会动吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.35,0:04:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且看到克莱兹曼侯爵哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.32,0:04:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突然说"我也要去"的人\N可是兰花喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.73,0:04:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？这个嘛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.83,0:04:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,话是没错啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.30,0:04:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯，没办法\N那就速战速决吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.11,0:04:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊...我们还是回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.41,0:04:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说这什么话？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.48,0:04:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"无论如何都要去"\N这不是你说的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.48,0:04:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是都没有半个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.98,0:04:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,破破烂烂的好可怕耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.41,0:04:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回忆小学是在哪里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.82,0:04:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.65,0:04:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兰花你不是知道吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.62,0:04:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么我非得知道不可呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.16,0:04:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身心健康梦想是宇宙飞行...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.46,0:05:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.83,0:05:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回忆...回忆小学...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.24,0:05:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像随时都会垮掉的校舍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.21,0:05:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里搞不好是海盗的隐匿处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.01,0:05:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.98,0:05:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那首校歌\N可能就是他们同伴间的暗号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.38,0:05:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.98,0:05:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚才的校歌是这间小学\N为了要引导我们来而放的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.16,0:05:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.36,0:05:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我们正在找这间小学啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.13,0:05:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还真是个乐观的孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.23,0:05:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小学又不是人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.70,0:05:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么可能会做那种事嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.34,0:05:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总之，既然来到这里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.20,0:05:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只好继续走下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.81,0:05:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等我，兰花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.31,0:05:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人在吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.48,0:05:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇！里面更破烂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.32,0:06:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出...出现了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.14,0:06:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兰花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.81,0:06:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兰花救命呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.48,0:06:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我自己也忙不过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.15,0:06:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你自己想办法解决吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.69,0:06:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想不出办法啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.89,0:06:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.70,0:06:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快！趁现在快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.67,0:06:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.60,0:06:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我痛得走不动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.54,0:06:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？受伤了吗？让我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.14,0:06:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么嘛，只是皮肉擦伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.48,0:06:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是好痛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.01,0:07:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这一点小伤还可以跑啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.58,0:07:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,痛得跑不了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.29,0:07:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌，还有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.12,0:07:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优，你明明还能跑嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.53,0:07:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对喔...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.36,0:07:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,气死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.36,0:07:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不能再跑快点吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.86,0:07:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没办法啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.13,0:07:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.20,0:07:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇，被兰花抱着跑\N轻松，轻松...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.67,0:07:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优，抓紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.25,0:07:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你几公斤啊？\N好重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.45,0:07:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太过份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.55,0:07:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是标准体重耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.36,0:07:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别哭啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.62,0:07:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,烦死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.86,0:07:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.80,0:07:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.61,0:08:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好累喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.58,0:08:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还以为死定了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.45,0:08:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，不过这样大概会瘦一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.85,0:08:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.16,0:08:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌\N又来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.07,0:08:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.30,0:08:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,振作点！梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.61,0:08:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么会这样子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.38,0:08:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优，不要死啊，梅尔优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.35,0:08:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不能死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.29,0:08:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.99,0:08:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到了吗？\N是我先打中敌人的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.53,0:08:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个比赛算我赢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.73,0:08:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼...输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.50,0:08:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小孩子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.97,0:09:02.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，不甘心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.10,0:09:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只差这么一点就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.64,0:09:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.74,0:09:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.84,0:09:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是游戏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.98,0:09:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,游戏？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.05,0:09:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把进入学校的人当成目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.55,0:09:16.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最先打倒目标的人胜利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.42,0:09:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,游戏？你们说这是游戏？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.32,0:09:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，很好玩呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.82,0:09:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次再玩一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.03,0:09:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.79,0:09:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们再怎么玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.73,0:09:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是得区分什么可以做\N什么不可以做呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.43,0:09:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玩游戏竟然还杀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.34,0:09:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们搞什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.07,0:09:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是，那是油漆弹啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.11,0:09:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？油漆弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.58,0:09:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊...真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.01,0:09:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优，你真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.75,0:09:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我真的以为死定了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.65,0:09:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，兰花你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.82,0:09:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这些小孩没有影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.59,0:09:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,脚也是透明的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.76,0:10:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们该不会是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.13,0:10:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,克莱兹曼先生的学生证...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.01,0:10:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,克莱兹曼先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.28,0:10:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让你们久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.62,0:10:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你回来啦，莱格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.46,0:10:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好慢喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.66,0:10:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.69,0:10:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,终于可以一起玩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.80,0:10:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,两位姊姊，谢谢你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.58,0:10:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个...莫非是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.55,0:11:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幽灵？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.52,0:11:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，小孩的幽灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.66,0:11:05.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那可能是集体幻觉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.96,0:11:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅尔优和兰花\N看到了相同的幻觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.43,0:11:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.80,0:11:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兰花，刚才明明看到...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.94,0:11:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任务完成，准备返回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.37,0:11:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.17,0:11:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兰花，为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.18,0:11:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样不是很好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.71,0:11:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,克莱兹曼侯爵的学生证\N也平安回到了小学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.25,0:11:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样就够了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.55,0:11:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对喔，说得也对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.92,0:11:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是小时候快乐的心\N还留在学校里玩耍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.63,0:11:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(下个菜单是\N佛特的遗迹炖煮麻烦酱菜)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.23,0:11:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.13,0:11:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不是很可爱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.37,0:11:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪里可爱了呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.60,0:11:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特，要不要抱抱看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.87,0:11:51.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.61,0:11:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不要客气没关系呀，请吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.54,0:11:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是跟你说过我不要吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.98,0:11:57.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎么流这么多汗呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.63,0:12:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,满天的星辰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.37,0:12:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像是打翻水瓶似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.61,0:12:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给我新月的曲线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.68,0:12:36.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做了梦之后，变得想见你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.25,0:12:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,侧耳倾听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.35,0:12:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看，不是听见了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.26,0:12:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令人兴奋的天线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.10,0:12:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要让它睡着  NO  NO
